msgctxt "sn56.57:0.2"
msgid "6. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "6. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 57. Paṭhamamahāsamuddasutta → samuddasuttaṃ (bj) | samudda 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.57:0.3"
msgid "57. Paṭhamamahāsamuddasutta "
msgstr "57. The Ocean (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.463, sc1
msgctxt "sn56.57:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso mahāsamuddato dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni uddharitāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose a man was to draw up two or three drops of water from the ocean. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.57:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.57:1.3"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yāni dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatāni, yaṃ vā mahāsamudde udakan”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the two or three drops drawn out or the water in the ocean?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.57:1.4"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ—mahāsamudde udakaṃ; appamattakāni dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatāni. "
msgstr "“Sir, the water in the ocean is certainly more. The two or three drops drawn out are tiny. "

msgctxt "sn56.57:1.5"
msgid "Saṅkhampi na upenti, upanidhampi na upenti, kalabhāgampi na upenti mahāsamudde udakaṃ upanidhāya dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatānī”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the water in the ocean, it can’t be reckoned or compared, it’s not even a fraction.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.57:1.6"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa … pe … "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.57:1.7"
msgid "yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.57:1.8"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

